\par\par \uc2 BUSSINESS\par \b \uc2 BI MAINTAINS BENCHMARK INTEREST RATE AT 3.5 PERCENT\b0\par\par\uc2 565 \uc2 words\par \uc2 20 April 2021\par \uc2 LKBN ANTARA\par \uc2 ANTARA\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2021. LKBN Antara \par \par \uc2 By Azis Kurmala\par \par \uc2 Jakarta (ANTARA) - The meeting of Board of Governors (RDG) of \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  (BI) \uc2 on April 19-20, 2021, reached a decision to maintain the benchmark interest rate, or the BI Seven-Day Reverse Repo Rate (BI7DRRR), at 3.5 percent.\par \par \uc2 "This decision is in line with the need to maintain stability of the rupiah exchange rate and safeguard it from the impact of high \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  in the global financial markets despite low inflation forecasts," BI Governor \uc2 Perry Warjiyo\uc2  stated at a virtual press conference in Jakarta, Tuesday.\par \par \uc2 Warjiyo also ensured that his party will unwaveringly support further national \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery by optimizing the accommodative monetary and macroprudential \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  mix and expediting digitization of the payment system.\par \par \uc2 The BI governor explained that support will be offered through nine steps, with the first being to strengthen the rupiah exchange rate \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  while holding ground in the market through triple intervention to maintain stability in the exchange rate in accordance with market fundamentals and mechanisms.\par \par \uc2 The second approach is to continue to bolster the monetary operation strategy to support the accommodative monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  stance.\par \par \uc2 The third step aims to increase the use of BI sukuk instruments (SukBI) in tenors of one week to 12 months in order to strengthen sharia monetary operations that have been in effect since April 16, 2021.\par \par \uc2 The fourth is to continue the accommodative macroprudential \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  by maintaining a countercyclical buffer (CCB) ratio at zero percent; a macroprudential liquidity buffer ratio (PLM) of six percent, with repo flexibility of six percent; and a sharia PLM ratio of 4.5 percent, with repo flexibility of 4.5 percent.\par \par \uc2 Fifth, strengthening transparency of the bank"s prime lending rate (SBDK) and continuing coordination with the government and relevant authorities to expedite transmission of the monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  through bank lending rates and increase credit and financing to the business world.\par \par \uc2 The sixth is to extend the validity period of the SKNBI pricing \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  of Rp1 from BI to banks and a maximum of Rp2,900 from banks to customers from initially ending June 30, 2021, to December 31, 2021, to support acceleration of the nation\u8217\'20\'19s \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery.\par \par \uc2 The seventh is to strengthen the QRIS \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  to encourage the acceleration of inclusive and efficient digitalization of the \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and finance by increasing the QRIS transaction limit, from Rp2 million to Rp5 million, effective from May 1, 2021.\par \par \uc2 The QRIS MDR \b \highlight22\uc2 tariff\b0 \highlight\uc2  reduction for merchants in the category of \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  service agencies (BLU) and \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  service obligation (PSO), from 0.7 percent to 0.4 percent, to take effect from June 1, 2021.\par \par \uc2 The eighth step pertains to ensuring security, reliability, smoothness, and availability of payment system services and rupiah currency management in the face of Eid al-Fitr 1442 H.\par \par \uc2 Lastly, facilitating the implementation of trade and investment promotions as well as disseminating information of the use of local currency settlement (\uc2 LCS\uc2 ) in collaboration with related agencies.\par \par \uc2 Investment and trade promotions will be held in Japan, Singapore, the United States, China, France, and the United Kingdom in April and May 2021.\par \par \uc2 Moreover, the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  decided to maintain the deposit facility rate at 2.75 percent and the lending facility rate to stay unchanged at 4.25 percent.\par \par \uc2 EDITED BY INE\par \par \uc2 (T.A063/A/H-SHT/H-SHT) 20-04-2021 18:36:10\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020210420eh4k000p1\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
