as required as a buffer to fulfill \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  requirements as well as to anticipate financial market developments.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CThe unspent funds are high in amount, but this is for buffer and to meet the needs of state \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2 . It also becomes the financial strategy to anticipate the inflation rising in the US that potentially leads to the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  of our financing,\u8221\'20\'1D she stated.\par \par \uc2 EDITED BY INE\par \par \uc2 (T.J010/B/H-SHT/H-SHT) 25-05-2021 18:58:40\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020210525eh5p000p1\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
