\par\par \b \uc2 Govt Asked to Enforce Lockdown in Bali for 14 Days\b0\par\par\uc2 294 \uc2 words\par \uc2 28 June 2021\par \uc2 Tempo.co\par \uc2 TEMPOE\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 Copyright 2021. PT Tempo Inti Media, Tbk \par \par \uc2 TEMPO.CO, Jakarta - Tourism observer Taufan Rahmadi suggested the government adopt New Zealand's strategies in reviving Bali tourism which was hit hard by the Covid-19 pandemic. According to him, the first stage is to enforce a lockdown for 14 days.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1COn level 1, I impose a lockdown in Bali for the next 14 days, \u8216\'20\'18Nyepikan Bali\u8217\'20\'19,\u8221\'20\'1D said Taufan in his statement on Monday, June 28.\par \par \uc2 At that stage, the government is asked to tighten the health protocols and encourage people to work from home. Schools and \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  areas must also be closed. After that, the government needs to undergo mass Covid-19 antigen tests for all residents.\par \par \uc2 Once the lockdown is over, the government can gradually reopen tourism starting from national flights to international ones. After these stages have been passed, Bali can then welcome tourists again.\par \par \uc2 Taufan argued that the government's plan to postpone the schedule for reopening Bali's international gates, which was scheduled to take place in July, due to the soaring Covid-19 cases, caused concerns. This \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  may worsen the region\u8217\'20\'19s \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 , which mostly relies on the tourism sector.\par \par \uc2 \u8220\'20\'1CMaking Bali in current \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  will further depress Bali\u8217\'20\'19s \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and further keep it far from the expected recovery targets,\u8221\'20\'1D Taufan added.\par \par \uc2 According to Taufan, the delay in reopening Bali tourism for foreign tourists should be a momentum to improve. Establishing Bali as a Covid-19 green zone or areas with low or zero virus transmission, could be done in stages, starting from at the village level, subdistrict, regency, up to provincial level.\par \par \uc2 Read: Bali to Welcome Tourists Soon as Covid-19 Vaccination Rate Hits 70%\par \par \uc2 FRANCISCA CHRISTY ROSANA\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://statik.tempo.co/data/2021/06/12/id_1027470/1027470_720.jpg"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Click here to view picture}}}\par \par \uc2 Document TEMPOE0020210628eh6s0008f\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
