 the \b \highlight22\uc2 tax\b0 \highlight\uc2  base.\par \par \uc2 Hence, it is most imperative for the government and the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2  to speed up their deliberation of the omnibus bill on \b \highlight22\uc2 taxes\b0 \highlight\uc2  so that all implementing regulations are in place for full-fledged enforcement by 2022.\par \par \uc2 Document JKPOST0020210630eh6u00005\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
