.\par \par \uc2 The government should also continue to improve the current account \b \highlight22\uc2 deficit\b0 \highlight\uc2  in collaboration with various stakeholders to accelerate the improvement of the nation\u8217\'20\'19s export performance, he said.\par \par \uc2 He then urged the government and the monetary authority to make optimum use of the present momentum, including the appreciation in the rupiah"s exchange rate and net inflows of foreign capital.\par \par \uc2 "The rising foreign exchange \b \highlight22\uc2 reserves\b0 \highlight\uc2  can maintain the sustainable stability of the rupiah"s exchange rate, in accordance with its fundamental value," he observed.\par \par \uc2 The government had earlier predicted the rupiah"s exchange rate would remain in the range of Rp13,900-Rp15,000 per US dollar under the KEM PPKP in the \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  year 2022.\par \par \uc2 (T.H-SHT/A/R013/R013) 30-06-2021 18:17:06\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020210630eh6u000rt\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
