e food sector as well as food storage and delivery areas.\par \par \uc2 Felippa went on to say that the government must also guarantee permits of operation not only for the basic food processing industry but also for the supporting industries once the PPKM Darurat is enforced.\par \par \uc2 Read Also: Reports Say Jokowi Will Enforce 'PPKM Darurat'\par \par \uc2 BISNIS.COM\par \par {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://statik.tempo.co/data/2021/06/30/id_1031630/1031630_720.jpg"}}{\fldrslt{\cf2 \uc2 Click here to view picture}}}\par \par \uc2 Document TEMPOE0020210701eh7100001\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
