ls are crucial to ensure the continuity of the people"s \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  and social activities, she said.\par \par \uc2 Furthermore, the House and the government have set the \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  capacity of the 2022 state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  draft to be able to anticipate the \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  of the pandemic, she said.\par \par \uc2 She then urged the government to focus \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  on handling the pandemic and maintaining the national social and \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery programs, including the absorption of local government budgets for the programs.\par \par \uc2 (T.KR-UYU/B/H-FDH/H-FDH) 06-08-2021 23:49:24\par \par \uc2 Document ANTARA0020210806eh86002mh\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
